<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/711078-how-long-did-the-author-stay-in-kalimpong">How long did the author stay in Kalimpong, where the story is based? The story is completely stereotyped within a certain phase which could give wrong impression to the reader, fiction might it be. Because I did my education in Kalimpong and I was very present during that time.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_711078'><a id="like_count_community_question_711078" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/711078?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F95186.The_Inheritance_of_Loss">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/711078-how-long-did-the-author-stay-in-kalimpong">5 years ago</a>
</li>
