<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/711077-how-long-did-the-author-stay-in-kalimpong">How long did the author stay in Kalimpong, where the story is based? The story is completely stereotyped within a certain phase which could give wrong impression to the reader, fiction might it be. Because I did my education in Kalimpong and I was very present during that time.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
